data.description: Elegant & modern home only 12 minutes to downtown Houston!  Luxury fixtures; high-end finishes throughout!  Large modern windows flood the living space with natural light.  Hugh back yard; pre-zoned for future guest house or detached garage with dwelling unit.  Polised concrete floors, marble waterfall countertop; stainless steel appliances.  Designer fixtures, tile and hardware throughout. Solar panels offset monthly utilitiy bills. Never suffer a freezing weather blackout again! Telsa Powerwall provides power during blackouts and city outages were they to occur!    Make this centrally located home yours! Priced to sell!  Arrange your viewing today!
